		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The first thing I noticed was the Readme is as big as the game <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />   Wow.
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle">Fx3 wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">- Not bad. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> Well, I am an adept of Asteroids' control scheme, as Up=speedUp, Down=breakes. Plus, the spaceship (?) sprite has a weird shooting - I never know exactly a straight fire while spinning. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /></div><br /><div class="quotetitle">Petruza wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">:cry: Don't like the control system.</div>
