		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Smash TV, the NES port of an arcade game using Robotron's control scheme, used the following control system:
<br />Control Pad: Move
<br />A: Shoot in movement-direction, and set B-direction to movement-direction
<br />B: Shoot in B-direction

		

